{ Followed by either consolidating with ...Nf6, or even ...e5 can be played, taking control over the center. In either case, Black's position is fine.   The following is just a demonstrative line:  14.e4  Trying to weaken the structure.  14...h6  15.Be3  Ba6  And Black is already doing perfectly.  16.a5  loses to  fxe4  17.Bxe4  d5  . }
