18. e7 Qxe7 19. O-O-O
{ 19.Rxh6  Kg7  followed by taking on e3 will lead to an endgame where Black cannot be worse. More critical is to hide the white king, but the position remains objectively equal, though playable for both sides after ...Qe6. }
19... Qe6 { The position is very dynamic and the stronger player will win! } *

