16. Bxa6 Nxa6
{ Black can also include the intermediate move  16...Nxe5  ,  but in my opinion, there is no reason to be afraid of the pawn sacrifice. }
17. Nxc6 Nf6
{ With huge compensation for the sacrificed pawn. White's king is on e1, and we have the e4-square for the knight; I would love to play such a position as Black! }
