8. Ng3 Nbd7 { Once again we are aiming for the ...e5 idea. } 9. Be2 e5
{ 9...dxc4  10.Bxc4  e5  leads to the same position. } 10. O-O exd4 11. exd4
{ This position is safe for Black, and we even have 2 options. } 11... dxc4
