{ This continuation does not change much the evaluation of the position. }
13... Qb8 14. a3
{ The move a3 seems to be the best defense against Backs' ...Nb4. } 14... Rd8
15. Kb1 Bg4
{ And after ...a6 Black wins back the d4-pawn, with a good position. } *

