13. Ne5 { The most aggressive move and also the most dangerous try. } 13...
Nxe5 14. dxe5 Nd7 { We have to be very exact during the next few moves. } 15.
f4
{ White would like to get a position after something like @@StartFEN@@r2q1rk1/1b1n1pp1/1pp1p2p/p2pP3/1PP2P2/P5P1/2QNP1BP/R4RK1 w - - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  16.cxd5  cxd5  and now Nf3-d4, where he could enjoy a big advantage. Black must act precisely to avoid White reaching his goals... }
