11... c5 { Our usual plan and it works here as well. } 12. cxd5 Bxd5 13. b3 Qe7
{ The a3-knight is badly placed and Black is completely out of danger. } 14.
Nc4 Rfd8
{ Successfully breaking out from the slight passivity, Black activates his rooks and solves all his opening problems. }
15. Qe3 Rac8 16. Rfc1 h6 { Wojtaszek-Yu Yangyi, Online game 2021. } *

